import React from "react"; import "./About.css"; export const About = () => (

About Us

This endeavour started in 2007, when I and my colleagues decided to show the world unique life and culture of Africa. We hold nature and ecology of this place very close to our hearts, so part of our profits goes to charity.

We have presence in many African countries, and we are ready to show you each one of them. They are all unique and interesting for everyone.

We are ready to show you the world... even more than that! We are ready to show you Africa! Come and join us!

);
